import {Card, Row, Col, Form} from "react-bootstrap";
import "./Search.css"


function Search() {
    return (
        <Card>
            <Card.Body>
                <Row>
                    <Form style={{display:"flex"}}>
                        <Col>
                            <Form.Group style={{marginRight:'5px',padding:"20px", textAlign:"center", border:"solid 1px rgb(220, 225, 230)", borderRadius:"6px"}} className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                                <Form.Label style={{fontWeight:"bold", color:"rgb(98 121 142)", marginBottom:"1.5rem"}}>Email address</Form.Label>
                                <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                                    <option>Chọn điểm khởi hành</option>
                                    <option value="1">One</option>
                                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                                </Form.Select>
                            </Form.Group>
                            
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Form.Group style={{marginRight:'5px',padding:"20px", textAlign:"center", border:"solid 1px rgb(220, 225, 230)", borderRadius:"6px"}} className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                                <Form.Label style={{fontWeight:"bold", color:"rgb(98 121 142)", marginBottom:"1.5rem"}}>Email address</Form.Label>
                                <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                                    <option>Chọn điểm đến</option>
                                    <option value="1">One</option>
                                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                                </Form.Select>
                            </Form.Group>
                        </Col>

                    </Form>
                    
                </Row>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default Search
